<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 12:34:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>蓝斑-杏仁核回路破坏前额叶控制以损害恐惧消退</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/locus-coeruleus-amygdala-circuit-disrupts-prefrontal-control-to-impair-fear-extinction</link><description>上周浏览次数最多的《美国国家科学院院刊》文章之一是“蓝斑-杏仁核回路破坏前额叶控制以损害恐惧消退”。在这里探索这篇文章： &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/locus-coeruleus-amygdala-circuit-disrupts-prefrontal-control-to-impair-fear-extinction2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 12:34:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/locus-coeruleus-amygdala-circuit-disrupts-prefrontal-control-to-impair-fear-extinction</guid></item><item><title>何时考虑无低钠血症的渗透性脱髓鞘综合征</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/when-to-consider-osmotic-demyelination-syndrome-without-hyponatremia</link><description>阅读这篇 Journal Watch 文章以及有关 NEJM Clinician 的更多临床总结。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/when-to-consider-osmotic-demyelination-syndrome-without-hyponatremia2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 12:19:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/when-to-consider-osmotic-demyelination-syndrome-without-hyponatremia</guid></item><item><title>糖尿病患者的肝硬化和全因死亡率</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/liver-stiffness-and-all-cause-mortality-in-individuals-with-diabetes</link><description>弹性成像发现的肝脏硬度与成人糖尿病患者死亡风险较高有关，这表明弹性成像可能有助于识别高风险个体。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/liver-stiffness-and-all-cause-mortality-in-individuals-with-diabetes2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 12:04:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/liver-stiffness-and-all-cause-mortality-in-individuals-with-diabetes</guid></item><item><title>权衡我们的太阳能社区</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/weighing-our-solar-neighborhood</link><description>测量称为脉冲星的恒星遗迹的加速度有助于研究人员绘制银河系区域质量的分布图。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/weighing-our-solar-neighborhood2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 11:49:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/weighing-our-solar-neighborhood</guid></item><item><title>构建更好、更精确的液滴</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/building-a-better-more-precise-droplet</link><description>一个不起眼的液滴可以成为从医学到制造等许多领域非常有用的工具。然而，控制液滴的大小是一项重要且非常棘手的任务。一组研究人员以前所未有的精度确定了液滴如何分解成更小的液滴、以什么尺寸以及在什么条件下分解。这项研究的结果是&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/building-a-better-more-precise-droplet2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 11:34:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/building-a-better-more-precise-droplet</guid></item><item><title>火星上埋藏三角洲的发现可能会促进对生命的搜寻</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-discovery-of-a-buried-delta-on-mars-could-boost-the-search-for-life</link><description>随着在地表深处发现了一个古老的河流三角洲，有更多的证据表明火星上曾经有水流动。 NASA 的毅力号火星车利用探地雷达在 Jezero 陨石坑下方超过 35 米处发现了它。毅力号于 2020 年发射，旨在寻找这颗红色星球上古代生命的迹象。自2021年2月着陆以来，它一直在探索杰泽罗陨石坑并收集岩石样本。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-discovery-of-a-buried-delta-on-mars-could-boost-the-search-for-life2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 11:19:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-discovery-of-a-buried-delta-on-mars-could-boost-the-search-for-life</guid></item><item><title>硬粒小麦品系将耐冻性与高品质面食结合在一起</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/durum-wheat-lines-combine-freezing-tolerance-with-high-pasta-quality</link><description>来自 Skoltech、墨西哥国际玉米和小麦改良中心、意大利谷物和工业作物研究中心以及其他国际组织的研究人员开发了新的硬质小麦品种，能够在冰冻温度下生存，同时保持优质面食生产所需的谷物质量。研究， &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/durum-wheat-lines-combine-freezing-tolerance-with-high-pasta-quality.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 11:04:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/durum-wheat-lines-combine-freezing-tolerance-with-high-pasta-quality</guid></item><item><title>DESI 绘制了 C-19，一条金属极其贫乏的银河系恒星流</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/desi-maps-c-19-an-extremely-metal-poor-milky-way-stellar-stream</link><description>一个国际天文学家小组使用基特峰国家天文台的 Mayall 4 米望远镜观测到了 C-19——银河系光晕中的一条金属极其贫乏的恒星流。观察活动的结果， &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/desi-maps-c-19-an-extremely-metal-poor-milky-way-stellar-stream2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 10:49:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/desi-maps-c-19-an-extremely-metal-poor-milky-way-stellar-stream</guid></item><item><title>在超酸性条件下工作的荧光染料扩大了极端环境下成像的可能性</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/fluorescent-dye-that-works-in-superacidic-conditions-expands-possibilities-for-imaging-in-extreme-environments</link><description>自 20 世纪 60 年代以来，硼二吡咯亚甲基染料（通常称为 BODIPY 染料）因其强荧光而被广泛应用，特别是在生物成像、分子和离子传感以及光敏剂方面。研究人员特别喜欢通过对 BODIPY 分子进行简单修改，可以调整其发射颜色——这是多色成像应用不可或缺的品质。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/fluorescent-dye-that-works-in-superacidic-conditions-expands-possibilities-for-imaging-in-extreme-environments2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 10:34:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/fluorescent-dye-that-works-in-superacidic-conditions-expands-possibilities-for-imaging-in-extreme-environments</guid></item><item><title>航天级钙钛矿太阳能电池可以承受极端的温度波动</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/space-grade-perovskite-solar-cells-can-survive-extreme-temperature-fluctuations</link><description>慕尼黑大学的艾丁集团推出了一项新策略，使钙钛矿太阳能电池能够更耐受极端温度波动。为此，慕尼黑大学化学与药学系组长 Erkan Aydin 博士领导的研究人员结合了两种分子方法。他们的目标是稳定钙钛矿材料内的晶粒结构和太阳能电池的界面，特别注重增强钙钛矿层和底层基板之间的相互作用。这使得太阳能电池能够在近地轨道（LEO）典型的极端热循环以及其他恶劣环境条件下保持稳定的性能。他们的结果是&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/space-grade-perovskite-solar-cells-can-survive-extreme-temperature-fluctuations2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 10:19:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/space-grade-perovskite-solar-cells-can-survive-extreme-temperature-fluctuations</guid></item></channel></rss>